	/**
	 * Supposed to hold the Angle of the next turn. <code>0°;</code> straight<br/>
	 * <code>+x°;</code> left turn (<code>0 < x <= 180</code>)<br/>
	 * <code>-x°;</code> right turn (<code>0 > x >= -180</code>)
	 */
